2	// handoff drain path, runs vsim, and expects:
3	//   - run() returns EXIT_HANDOFF_TO_QEMU (200)
4	//   - state.bin is written with valid magic and gpr[12] == 3
5	// The QEMU spawn half lives in the round-trip e2e test.
